OL,3,CITV News cameras catch 200 cyclists
OL,4,Crunning a red light in just one hour
OL,6,FVideo report by Rags Martel
OL,8,FWords by ITV News Assistant Producer
OL,9,FEva Carroll
OL,11,FITV News cameras have caught 200
OL,12,Fcyclists jumping red lights at rush
OL,13,Fhour in the space of just 60 minutes.
OL,15,FWe monitored a busy cycle Lane on
OL,16,FVictoria Embankment opposite
OL,17,FBlackfriars station between 8:20am and
OL,18,F9:20am.
