OL,3,CITV News cameras catch 200 cyclists
OL,4,Crunning a red light in just one hour
OL,6,FOn average three to four cyclists
OL,7,Fignored red lights every minute and
OL,8,Fmore than half failed to stop.
OL,10,FTransport for London advises cyclists
OL,11,Fto follow the Highway Code and warns
OL,12,Fcyclists may be fined #50 for going
OL,13,Fthrough a red light.
OL,15,FSince the start of 2025, 284 cyclists
OL,16,Fin the City of London have been fined
OL,17,Ffor failing to stop at lights.
