OL,6,FGerard Griffiths is a road safety
OL,7,Fcampaigner and says that more needs to
OL,8,Fbe done to make dangerous cyclists
OL,9,Frealise the potentially fatal
OL,10,Fconsequences of their actions.
OL,12,FHe said: "There's a reason why cars
OL,13,Fand motorbikes and lorries stop at red
OL,14,Flights - because they have to.
OL,16,F"They know there are consequences if
OL,17,Fthey go through them. Bikes just don't
OL,18,Fseem to have that same sort of
OL,19,Fattitude or people that cycle."
