OL,6,FGerard's mum died after colliding with
OL,7,Fa cyclist travelling at 29mph in a
OL,8,F20mph zone in Regent's Park.
OL,10,FCycling has boomed in popularity in
OL,11,FLondon over recent years and is a
OL,12,Fclean and efficient mode of transport.
OL,14,FSimon Munk from London Cycling
OL,15,FCampaign told ITV News London that
OL,16,Fsome of the cycling lanes in London
OL,17,Fare overcapacity and says
OL,18,Fstatistically more pedestrians ignore
OL,19,Ftraffic signals.
