OL,6,F"I think it's important to understand
OL,7,Fthat we shouldn't be accepting
OL,8,Fcyclists jumping red lights, but we
OL,9,Fshould be working out why. We should
OL,10,Fbe working out what the problem is and
OL,11,Ffixing it," he said.
OL,13,F"This is annoying, and it's really
OL,14,Fdeeply hostile to pedestrians. These
OL,15,Fpeople shouldn't be doing it, but it's
OL,16,Fnot actually statistically very
OL,17,Fdangerous," Mr Munk added.
