OL,6,FCyclists are responsible for fewer
OL,7,Fthan 1% of the pedestrian deaths on
OL,8,FBritish roads and they are far more
OL,9,Flikely to be killed than to kill,
OL,10,Faccording to campaign group Cycling UK.
OL,12,FA bill is currently going through
OL,13,Fparliament to bring the 1861 law up to
OL,14,Fdate.
OL,16,FUnder the current law, if cyclists
OL,17,Fstrike and kill a pedestrian,
OL,18,Foffenders can be imprisoned for no
OL,19,Fmore than two years under the ancient
OL,20,Flaw.
