OL,6,FThe proposed amendment to the Criminal
OL,7,FJustice Bill means dangerous cyclists
OL,8,Fcould face up to 14 years in prison.
OL,10,FTory MP Iain Duncan Smith has
OL,11,Fcampaigned on the issue and said the
OL,12,Fproposal was not "anti-cycling" but is
OL,13,Fintended to ensure safety and
OL,14,Faccountability on the roads.
OL,16,FITV News spoke to pedestrians,
OL,17,Fmotorists, and cyclists who all agreed
OL,18,Fon one thing - that more needs to be
OL,19,Fdone to ensure people obey the rules
OL,20,Fof the road.
